item.title: Videos of Google IO 2011 – Android Tracks of Day One
item.description: Google IO is currently taking place in San Francisco and for everybody who could not attend Google live streamed quite some sessions. In the following you can see the videos which are currently published: Google I/O 2011: Android Keynote Day One [youtube OxzucwjFEEs] As an Android developer I am very interested in the Android sessions as you can imagine. So the following the next video first covers advaced topics of android development.
